     C                     PARM           PZKHIN 12
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    O@HDK   3
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    PZBMON
     C                     MOVE 'HD '     PZKOTE
     C                     CALL 'AAMRS9'  AAMRS9
     C           PZBMON    IFNE *BLANK
     C                     MOVE PZKIBN    O@HDK
     C                     END
      *
